    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Budget-Friendly & Honestly Priced \u2013 A Fixer or Basic Runner! \ud83d\ude97\n\nLooking for bare-bones, affordable transportation? This vehicle is priced to reflect its current condition \u2014 it has seen better days and shows its age with visible wear, mechanical quirks, and cosmetic issues. It may suit a handy buyer looking for a project, a parts car, or simply the most economical way to get from A to B without high expectations. No surprises here \u2014 what you see is what you get, and the price reflects every bit of that honesty! Come take a look and decide for yourself.",
