    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed honestly as a good-condition car, making it a dependable and practical choice for buyers seeking reliable used transportation. The exterior presents well overall, with only minor cosmetic blemishes such as light surface scratches and perhaps a small scuff or two \u2014 nothing that detracts significantly from its appearance. The paint retains good luster, the body panels are straight, and there are no signs of major accident damage or rust. Mechanically, the car runs smoothly and has been maintained to a reasonable standard; you can expect reliable day-to-day performance without immediate concerns. The interior is clean and functional, showing normal wear consistent with regular use \u2014 think slightly worn seat fabric or minor marks on trim pieces, but nothing broken or heavily damaged. All major systems including engine, transmission, brakes, and climate control are in good working order. This is a solid, honest used car that should serve its next owner well without surprise repair bills on the horizon.",
      "price": 32000.0,
